race.comment: MR MACHUPICCHU (5) continued the encouraging form and wasn't far away last time when second over 1207m at Del Mar. Overdue and gets his chance. NO MORE DING DONGS (6) finished out of the money two starts back then was beaten 5 lengths when seventh in a 1106m contest at Del Mar seven-and-a-half weeks ago. Ideally placed and is sure to be there at the finish. ARIO (3) started at $5.73 last time and ran below expectations, finishing fifth and beaten 10 lengths at Emerald Downs (Dirt) over 1207m. Finds a nice race and can atone. COACH CRONIN (7) has switched yards since finishing third five weeks ago over 1207m at Del Mar.
